news.news: Monk provided 23 points (8-25 FG, 1-9 3Pt, 6-7 FT), five rebounds, six assists and two steals over 49 minutes during Monday's 123-118 double-overtime win over the Heat.
news.analysis: Monk didn't have his best shooting line after needing 25 shots to score 23 points, though he still posted an impressive line in general. He's been playing at a high level of late and has reached the 20-point mark in five of his last six outings. Monk should continue to have elevated usage as long as De'Aaron Fox (hip) remains sidelined.
